body:
PICTURES OF SPIDERMAN

What’s most interesting about J Jonah Jameson is that he differs so much between marvel universes. I did some research a while back and discovered he doesn’t always want PICTURES OF SPIDERMAN. I made this list of the wide variety of J. Jonahs Jameson:

In a universe where JJJ is best friends with the webslinger instead of his nemesis, he’s always really excited about PICTURES WITH SPIDERMAN.

In a universe where he’s the freelance photographer selling his work to Peter Parker, he takes PICTURES FOR SPIDERMAN.

A JJJ in a universe where he’s an arachnologist wants PICTURES OF SPIDERS.

In a universe where he’s doing an art installation about unmarried women, he wants PICTURES OF SPINSTERS.

In a universe where he’s running counterespionage, he wants PICTURES OF SPIES.

In a universe where he studies back injuries, he wants PICTURES OF SPINES.

In a universe where he teaches breakdancing, he wants PICTURES OF SPINNING MEN.

In a universe where he shoots gay pornography, he wants PICTURES OF NAKED MEN.

In a universe where he’s a pastor, he wants SCRIPTURES OF THE SON OF MAN.

In universe 692-a, Spiderman has been reduced to a liquid state by a supervillain’s attack, and JJJ has his people collect PITCHERS OF SPIDERMAN.

In a universe where he’s managing a baseball team that’s competing against the Avengers, he wants PITCHERS FOR SPIDERMAN.

In a universe where he’s a supervillain developing carnivorous plants to defeat his nemesis, he wants PITCHER-PLANTS FOR SPIDERMAN.

In a universe where he’s Peter Parker’s butler, he makes sure to always have PILLOWS FOR SPIDERMAN.

Later in that same universe, when the webslinger contracts a disease, JJJ makes sure to have PILLS FOR SPIDERMAN.

And when he needs to fight a duel, he gets PISTOLS FOR SPIDERMAN.

And when Peter Parker takes up botany and wants his plants to germinate, he gets PISTILS FOR SPIDERMAN.

In a universe where Parker comes out as trans, he gets PINAFORES FOR SPIDERMAN. (we’re still on the butler AU)

Of course, when she’s transitioning, JJJ gets her her hormones, in the form of PILL BOTTLES OF SPIRONOLACTONE.

And then, to document the transition, the JJJ of the butler-to-trans-peter-parker universe takes PICTURES OF SPIDERMAN.
